Author: ThatChicBitch
Text: I mean, if you stick it in a glass and add a 1/4 or 1/2 cup of Halo Top Vanilla Bean ice cream to it then you've basically got a pretty filling and not overly calorific Coke Float right there. I'd do it, tbh. Hell, I think I just talked myself into buying some Vanilla Coke Zero and Halo Top just thinking about it (woo, add some oatmeal on the side and I've got my OMAD for the day, too!)
